{"tid":1190044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：《蘋果》六四頭版 登法電視台 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-06-07T06:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T06:15:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9165bf89228333c8c187317bfe4affc8b4eb5f53","tid":1190044,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T06:15:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190607/20697657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F20697657&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ugKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=72f93c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190607%2F20697657&h=a0abff6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190607/20697657</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：《蘋果》六四頭版 登法電視台 - 李八方<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190607/large/a1404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190607%2Flarge%2Fa1404a.gif&h=4e230fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n18萬人六四夜喺維園舉起燭光，燭海唔止照亮香港，仲傳送到外地。外媒紛紛報道六四夜港人嗰種堅持，而《蘋果日報》前日以「18萬人悼六四」為題嘅A1頭版都喺法國廣受歡迎嘅法國電視一台電視節目《Quotidien（每日）》亮相，個節目仲影咗香港其他媒體報道六四，同埋比較中港，指出只有港媒可報道六四。不過節目只開名提《蘋果》報道咗六四燭光集會同有幾多人出席，仲唯一用特效將條題改做法文（圖），令法國觀眾知道香港人30年來，毋忘六四。  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：冇飯盒冇津貼 泛民出大巴接送街坊 (李八方)"}]}